resources FI(6)
notes
Two satellites, Swarm-B and ePOP fly over TRO and ESR as follows: 12 Nov: Only
Swarm-B: 20:35 UT; 13 Nov Swarm-B: 20:16 UT, ePOP: 20:19 UT; 14 Nov Swarm-B:
19:57 UT, ePOP: 19:55 UT. We want to study auroral electrodynamics by
simultaneous mainland and ESR measurements by using vertical tri-static VHF for
EF, F-A UHF, and ESR (fixed direction 32 m + 42 m). No simultaneous heating.
